1. show bgp evpn summary
    - view the overlay BGP neighbors (similar to show ip bgp summary for the underlay)
2. show bgp evpn route-type mac-ip
    - For viewing EVPN Type-2 advertisements
3. show bgp evpn route-type mac-ip <MAC> detail
4. show bgp evpn route-type ip-prefix ipv4
    - For viewing EVPN Type-5 advertisements
5. show bgp evpn route-type ip-prefix <SUBNET> detail
6. show bgp neighbors x.x.x.x (underlay next-hop) evpn received-routes detail 
7. show bgp neighbors x.x.x.x (underlay next-hop) evpn advertised-routes detail 
8. show vxlan config-sanity
9. show vxlan address-table
10. show vxlan vtep
11. show vxlan vni
12. show arp remote
13. show bgp debug policy inbound neighbor x.x.x.x evpn ...
14. show bgp evpn sanity detail
